query:
INSERT INTO checklistItemResults (taskChecklistId, templateItemId, result, photoUrls)
SELECT 
  30001 as taskChecklistId,
  cti.id as templateItemId,
  'na' as result,
  NULL as photoUrls
FROM taskChecklists tc
JOIN checklistTemplateItems cti ON cti.templateId = tc.templateId
WHERE tc.id = 30001
ORDER BY cti.order;
